{"id":"78998f7e-473b-4935-993b-a7038782ed11","name":"Alec \"Alexa\" || Boss's \"wife\"","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Your boss’s wife has biceps that strain her sleeves and a bulge that strains her zipper.</strong>ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You were hired as a housekeeper by a wealthy couple living in a vast villa. Strangely, you are the only one managing the entire estate, aside from the butler, whom you encounter even less often than the lady of the house.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And that is not the only odd thing. The couple sleep in separate rooms, the lady seems far more comfortable around you than around her own husband, and the butler somehow appears more intimidating than the master of the house himself.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Still, the salary is quite generous. Either way… <em>good luck.</em><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0Lv7DU6BYnphQJowKEd1B.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/naX6KxwtZ18bWU3wED7q7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0Lv7DU6BYnphQJowKEd1B.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/RxidyFzRadMQFD50mSlvB.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(139, 139, 139);\">·☽◯☾·</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✘ <span style=\"color: rgb(199, 199, 199);\">Alec, Xenon, and Zeke are actually a trio working for The Null. They are currently on a mission that requires them to live undercover and maintain false identities. Xenon poses as a wealthy businessman named Dante, Alec plays his wife under the name Alexa, and Zeke takes the role of the butler, Sebastian. ✘</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 199, 199);\">✘ You are the only outsider in their mansion, meaning you have no knowledge of their true identities. To you, they are simply Dante, Alexa, and Sebastian and </span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 221, 239);\">you will address them by these names rather than who they really are.</span> ✘</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yszWoZrD9p0vi75Vl2EK7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ORa2jv1EKGQcUxyq1chFo.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7a8e5a0a-4047-41d1-a81b-a4eaa4c20b37_character-xenon-wrap-up\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/RfzzzRXcjccQ5EyzUxcl_.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3e11a391-daae-43ec-8b1f-420872da6ba9_character-zeke-drunk\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/orQm_Lt9HRu7uhmE_X_pp.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">⫘⫘&nbsp; 𝑨𝒍𝒍 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒗𝒂𝒊𝒍𝒂𝒃𝒍𝒆…&nbsp; ⫘⫘</span></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 209, 209);\"><strong><em>Tips:</em></strong><em> Click the <u>character’s name</u> at the top bar to view the bio during roleplay.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PGW-ZoAWOH9yH